list.definition:
select CONCAT(upper(host),'__',severidade,'__',evento,'__',mensagem,'__',clock,'__',uf,'__',name) 
from (
     select t.host,t.severidade,t.evento, regexp_replace(a.message, '[^\w]+',' ','g') as mensagem,t.clock,t.uf,t.name as name
     from (  
          select t.eventid,t.host, e.severity as severidade, t.evento, to_timestamp(e.clock) as clock, t.uf,t.name
          from (
               select distinct t.eventid,t.host,t.evento, t.uf,t.name
               from (
                    select distinct e.eventid, t.host, e.name as evento, t.uf,t.name
                    from (
                         select distinct
                                t.triggerid
                              , h.hostid
                              , h.host
                              , split_part(g.name,'/',3) as uf
                              , h.name as name
                           from hosts h, hosts_groups hg, hstgrp g, items i, functions f, triggers t
                          where t.triggerid = f.triggerid
                            and f.itemid = i.itemid
                            and i.hostid = h.hostid
                            and h.hostid = hg.hostid
                            and h.maintenance_status = 0
                            and hg.groupid = g.groupid
                            and g.name ~ '^WAN/MODELO/'
                            and (h.status,i.status) = (0,0)
                            and t.status = 0
                            and t.value = 1
                            and t.priority in (4,5)
                            and i.name ~* '^(Ping para interface|ICMP - Ping)'
                    ) t, events e
                    where t.triggerid = e.objectid
                      and e.severity in (4,5)
                      and e.value = 1
                      and e.source = 0
                      and to_timestamp(e.clock) between (now() - interval '720 day') and now()
                      and e.name ~* '^(Ping para interface|Dispositivo.*indisponível)'
               ) t left join event_recovery r on r.eventid = t.eventid
               where r.r_eventid is null
          ) t, events e
          where e.eventid = t.eventid
     ) t left join acknowledges a on a.eventid = t.eventid
     order by t.host, t.clock desc
) t --where mensagem ~* '^(PROBLEM|RI_)'

list.definition:
select distinct concat (upper(h.host), '____', h.maintenance_status)
  from host_inventory hi, hosts h, interface int, hosts_groups hg, hstgrp g
 where (hi.hostid,h.hostid,int.hostid,hg.hostid) = (h.hostid,int.hostid,hg.hostid,hi.hostid)
   and hg.groupid = g.groupid
   and lower(hi.type) = 'roteador'
   and h.status = 0
   and g.name ~ '^WAN/MODELO/$uf'
   and h.name !~ 'EADI|MPLS|SERPRO'
   and h.name ~ '^[A-Z]{2}(-|_)'
   and h.maintenance_status = 1

   order by 1;
